m. This paper describes the concept of interferometer link, designed\nhardware, basic control algorithms and performance evaluation results. The link\nprototype was built to distribute 1.3 GHz signal through a coaxial cable.\nMeasured phase drift suppression factor value exceeded level of 100.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 24 Jun 2018 19:40:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-26"}
